snippet.title: Warhammer Online Prod. Podcast #15 - Old School Podcastin'
snippet.description: Paul and Josh are kickin' it old-school around the kitchen table talking about the latest and greatest in WAR. From armor dies to siege equipment, from the campaign map to city siege testing, this podcast is packed full of golden nuggets of information. Don't miss it!
